data.description: This beautiful home boasts stunning sunset views from its sunporch and a spacious backyard, fully fenced for privacy. With 4 full baths, 1 half bath, and 4 bedrooms plus a bonus room over the garage, there is ample space for a growing family or guests. The open kitchen and breakfast area is the perfect gathering spot, with enough room for everyone. The 2 upstairs bedrooms, each with its own on-suite, provide split floor plans for added privacy. The home also features ample storage options, from the garage to the attic, with large closets in many rooms. New roof being installed Aug 2023. Located just a few miles from the Tryon International Equestrian Center, this home is a great option for a full-time residence or a lucrative Air B&B opportunity. Enjoy peace and quiet in the country while taking advantage of the highly-rated Polk County School System. Don't miss this opportunity!
